<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095341>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–19. Dorsal view of head: 11, Renda bicarinata; 12, R. flagellicornis; 13, R. julietae; 14, R. fasciata; 15, R. sharpi; 16, R. leprieuri; 17, R. nitida; 19, R. fimetaria; 19, R. ophthalmica." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095341/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095344>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–24.Ventral view of head: 20, Philonthus testaceipennis; 21, Plochionocerus splendens; 22, Renda brendelli; 23, R. clavicornis; 24, R. brachyptera." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095344/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095346>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25–34. Lateral view of head: 25, Philonthus testaceipennis; 26, Agrodes conicicollis; 27, Renda debilis; 28, R. brachyptera; 29, R. fasciata; 30, R. profundepunctata; 31, R. leprieuri; 32, R. flagellicornis; 33, R. julietae; 34, R. bicarinata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095346/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095352>
    dc:description "FIGURES 53–61. Labrum: 53, Philonthus testaceipennis; 54, Renda spp. 55, R. fasciata. Lateral view of pronotal hypomeron: 56, Plochionocerus splendens; 57, Agrodes spp.; 58, Renda spp. 59, Elytra of Plochionocerus spp. Tibiae: 60, Agrodes spp.; 61, Plochionocerus spp. and Renda spp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095348>
    dc:description "FIGURES 35–46. Maxillary palpi: 35, Philonthus testaceipennis; 36, Agrodes conicicollis; 37, Plochionocerus splendens. Apical and subapical maxillary palpomeres: 38, R. bicarinata; 39, R. fimetaria; 40, R. minor. Labial palpi: 41, P. testaceipennis; 42, A. conicicollis. Apical and subapical labial palpomeres: 43, P. splendens; 44, R. formicaria; 45, R. brasiliana; 46, R. palpalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095348/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095350>
    dc:description "FIGURES 47–52. Pronotum: 47, Philonthus testaceipennis; 48, Plochionocerus splendens; 49, Renda formicaria; 50, R. glabrinotum; 51, R. fulgida; 52, R. minor." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095350/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095337>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Habitus, dorsal view: 1, Philonthus testaceipennis; 2, Plochionocerus splendens; 3, Renda brachyptera; 4, R. flagellicornis; 5, R. leprieuri; 6, R. debilis. Scale bar 3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095337/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095356>
    dc:description "FIGURES 78–92. Ventral view of aedeagus: 78, R. debilis; 79, R. lescheni; 80, R. longiceps; 81, R. mesoamericana; 82, R. minor; 83, R. nitida; 84, R. raulmunizi; 85, R. brendelli; 86, R. cariniventris; 87, R. clavicornis; 88, R. fimetaria; 89, R. fimetariamimus; 90, R. pronotalis; 91, R. julietae; 92, R. ophthalmica. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095356/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

